{"tid":797095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿乞丐乞討 大隻佬男模油站用棍打死佢","createTime":"2018-08-28T08:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T03:47:57.000Z","uid":82917,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e46938d164911ddf8d9ec7135f3013f32ca635a2","tid":797095,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"美國佛羅里達州邁阿密（Miami）一名32歲的健身模特兒在油站內，拒絕一名前來乞討的乞丐後，再用棍子打死他。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/164712_b28ee956ebafbc6976704faa50e01811.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F164712_b28ee956ebafbc6976704faa50e01811.png&h=50aa745e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被告岡薩雷斯（Hivo Gonzalez）亦有經營釣魚團，他涉嫌於6月一個晚上，在油站內襲擊一名前來行乞的男子克魯茲（Pedro Cruz）。油站內閉路電視片段拍到，事發前岡薩雷斯與克魯茲在吵架，然後岡薩雷斯走回車上，拿出一支敲魚棍，上前襲擊克魯茲。欲走避的克魯茲後腦被擊中，岡薩雷斯仍追上他再重擊一下，克魯茲隨即跌倒，趴在地上一動不動。<br />\n<br />\n岡薩雷斯後來與友人趕回車上開車離去，他翌日被捕。他稱當時相信自己如果不先動手，就會被克魯茲襲擊，他辯護律師指︰「他是一個很有教養的人，而他相信當時自己處於生命受威脅的情況。」<br />\n<br />\n警方的報告指，岡薩雷斯襲擊克魯茲後，既沒有求救，也沒有報警。法庭周五公開事發時的閉路電視片段，岡薩雷斯被控2級謀殺，一旦罪成將面臨10年監禁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72cfcb88c65e2420466bccf3a23ee89cd772ecf9","tid":797095,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:47:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180827/58609360\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180827%2F58609360&d=VNmlqQ1PE7hT5e2WvJGzcb5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=1069f76b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180827%2F58609360&h=b878de32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/arti